="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/incoming-palestinian-pm-forms-new-cabinet-in-west-bank-amid-wartime-economic-devastation/0000018e-890f-d782-a7bf-df3f6bb50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列面临的生存问题正走向爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/the-existential-issues-facing-israel-are-heading-towards-explosion/0000018e-8612-d641-abee-cfb78d820000</link><description>经过一年空前的冲突和抗议之后，大多数以色列人认为，纠正基本的司法、民事和安全问题对于国家的生存至关重要。正如内塔尼亚胡政府所希望的那样，让它们继续恶化可能会致命</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:28:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/the-existential-issues-facing-israel-are-heading-towards-explosion/0000018e-8612-d641-abee-cfb78d820000</guid></item><item><title>现代启示录：内塔尼亚胡除了无休止的谎言和脾气之外别无他法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/apocalypse-now-netanyahu-has-nothing-left-to-offer-but-endless-lies-and-temper-tantrums/0000018e-86a8-d9dd-a39f-ceea6d9d0000</link><description>以色列总理本周无法停止撒谎——对美国人、极端正统派和被绑架的以色列人的家人——但他对北方局势的沉默最能说明问题。正统派选民与代表他们的政党之间的关系</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 03:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/apocalypse-now-netanyahu-has-nothing-left-to-offer-but-endless-lies-and-temper-tantrums/0000018e-86a8-d9dd-a39f-ceea6d9d0000</guid></item><item><title>半年后，10 月 7 日谜题的部分内容仍在拼凑起来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/parts-of-oct-7-puzzle-coming-together-half-year-later/0000018e-869e-d0d3-a98e-d6ffa4d00000</link><description>哈马斯袭击以色列南部六个月后，很明显，那天发生的极端事件在战前几乎没有被军方排练过</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/parts-of-oct-7-puzzle-coming-together-half-year-later/0000018e-869e-d0d3-a98e-d6ffa4d00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡批准以色列代表团前往开罗和多哈恢复人质释放谈判</